  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. These are the device's own rendered frames; the DREAM\n     hero is a real photo of the 320×240 display glowing on your desk (it's on the\n     Photo Day list). Draft until then. -->\n<p class=\"\">A networked <strong class=\"\">320×240 pixel display that sits on my desk</strong> and shows me my own life in the Vulpes palette. It's an ESP32-S3-BOX-3B running an Arduino REST API, driven by a little bash CLI that rotates through \"scenes\" pulled from my personal data — gear, films, books, weather, typing speed, drafts, the wiki, todos — every 15 minutes.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Today&#x27;s weather as a desk-display scene\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/weather.png\" alt=\"Today&#x27;s weather as a desk-display scene\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/weather.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/weather.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/weather.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/weather.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Today&#x27;s weather as a desk-display scene\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.82deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Today's weather as a desk-display scene</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The last film I watched, with my rating\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/last-film.png\" alt=\"The last film I watched, with my rating\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/last-film.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/last-film.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/last-film.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/last-film.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The last film I watched, with my rating\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.28deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The last film I watched, with my rating</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">Each scene is a tiny self-contained script that fetches from a data source and draws with primitives (<code class=\"md-inline-code\">pixel</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">rect</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">circle</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">text</code>) over HTTP. A morning greeting; the current temperature; the book I'm reading; my best typing speed; a random gear card; a line from my journal. The whole thing is a calm, glanceable ambient display — the opposite of a notification feed.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A random gear card\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/gear.png\" alt=\"A random gear card\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/gear.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/gear.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/gear.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/gear.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A random gear card\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.02deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A random gear card</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Best WPM, pulled from my typing stats\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/wpm.png\" alt=\"Best WPM, pulled from my typing stats\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/wpm.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/wpm.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/wpm.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/wpm.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Best WPM, pulled from my typing stats\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.24deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Best WPM, pulled from my typing stats</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The book I&#x27;m currently reading\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/reading.png\" alt=\"The book I&#x27;m currently reading\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/reading.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/reading.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/reading.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/reading.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The book I&#x27;m currently reading\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The book I'm currently reading</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Morning greeting\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/greeting.png\" alt=\"Morning greeting\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/greeting.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/greeting.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/greeting.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/greeting.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Morning greeting\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.13deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Morning greeting</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"how-it-works\">How it works</h2>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Firmware</strong> — an Arduino sketch (LovyanGFX on the ESP32-S3-BOX-3B) exposes a small drawing REST API: <code class=\"md-inline-code\">/pixel</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">/rect</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">/circle</code>, <code class=\"md-inline-code\">/text</code>, plus a browser drawing UI served at <code class=\"md-inline-code\">/</code>.</li>\n<li class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">CLI</strong> — <code class=\"md-inline-code\">pixel &#x3C;scene></code> pings the device, then runs the scene script; every draw command is also logged so a companion renderer (<code class=\"md-inline-code\">pixel-render</code>) can snapshot exactly what's on the screen to a PNG. (The images on this page are those snapshots.)</li>\n<li class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Rotation</strong> — a launchd job picks a scene every 15 minutes, so the display keeps cycling through my data on its own.</li>\n</ul>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A todo scene\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/todos.png\" alt=\"A todo scene\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/todos.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/todos.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/todos.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/todos.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A todo scene\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A todo scene</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Clock\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/clock.png\" alt=\"Clock\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/clock.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/clock.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/clock.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/clock.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Clock\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.96deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Clock</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">There are scenes for nearly every corner of my data — a random old tweet, a draft note pulled from Obsidian, this week's intelligence-summary wiki page, today's site analytics, a line of cipher text, and a quiet field of ambient dots when there's nothing to say.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A random tweet from the archive\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/tweet.png\" alt=\"A random tweet from the archive\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/tweet.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/tweet.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/tweet.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/tweet.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A random tweet from the archive\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.04deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A random tweet from the archive</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A draft note pulled from Obsidian\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/draft.png\" alt=\"A draft note pulled from Obsidian\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/draft.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/draft.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/draft.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/draft.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A draft note pulled from Obsidian\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A draft note pulled from Obsidian</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"This week&#x27;s intelligence-summary wiki page\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/wiki.png\" alt=\"This week&#x27;s intelligence-summary wiki page\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/wiki.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/wiki.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/wiki.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/wiki.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"This week&#x27;s intelligence-summary wiki page\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">This week's intelligence-summary wiki page</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Today&#x27;s site analytics\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/umami.png\" alt=\"Today&#x27;s site analytics\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/umami.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/umami.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/umami.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/umami.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Today&#x27;s site analytics\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.99deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Today's site analytics</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A line of cipher text\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/cipher.png\" alt=\"A line of cipher text\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/cipher.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/cipher.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/cipher.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/cipher.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A line of cipher text\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.63deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A line of cipher text</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Ambient dots\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/ambient-dots.png\" alt=\"Ambient dots\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/pixel-canvas/ambient-dots.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/pixel-canvas/ambient-dots.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/pixel-canvas/ambient-dots.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/pixel-canvas/ambient-dots.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Ambient dots\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×480\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Ambient dots</figcaption>\n</figure>",
